data.text:
Misrata, Libya

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 32.377533, 15.092017.

One of the largest cities in Libya, Misrata is located on the coastal territory and has the population of about 285,000 people. It is one of the most favorite tourists spots and destination of many guests of the country. A historic city with the abundance of historic monuments, beautiful local architecture, gardens and parks, modern cinemas and shopping malls is a wonderful place for spending some days and exploring new cultures.
